originalText.text: It was such a pleasure to work with Jess! My wife and I were so unbelievably happy that we chose Jessica Schmitt Photography to photograph our wedding and our engagement session in Prospect Park. Combing through many photographers in NYC, Jess stood out with her natural, gorgeous photos and feel that we 100% made the BEST choice. We were so incredibly thrilled with how every single photo turned out — we get countless compliments on our photos. Jess (and Eric) captured the emotion and essence of a day we will remember for a lifetime. We love how all of our photos are very natural — not overly edited — and feel authentic and classy. Jess has an amazing eye for detail and is so incredibly talented, which was evident in every photo. Also, her amazingly calm demeanor really helped taking photos amidst family chaos, which made it so much easier on us. We feel very fortunate to have chosen Jess as our photographer and wholeheartedly recommend using her! She's the very best!!!

originalText.text: We absolutely loved having Jess as our photographer! She is such a warm and generous person, and made the whole process easy for us from start to finish. We received our photos quickly and she was great about communicating with us at every step. They turned out so well! And she took great pictures of our dog too!

originalText.text: Jessica was so great to work with. She shot both our engagement photos and our wedding and did a phenomenal job. She was able to coach us on how to move and interact for the photos in a way that felt really natural. We both look back and think about how much fun we had taking our photos and how Jess really put us at ease. She answered all of our questions up front and helped us think through things we had not even considered. She has a ton of experience, loves her job, and it shows! We would love to work with her again sometime in the future.

originalText.text: A good friend recommended Jess to me and my husband when we were looking for engagement photographers. Luckily we were able to work with her for both our engagement shoot and for our wedding. She has a real eye for taking beautiful photos and was great at guiding us on how to interact and move but still made the whole process feel very natural and special. Our photos from both occasions are beautiful and we would jump at the chance to work with Jess again if she’s available to capture another phase in our life together, like when our family starts to grow. Lastly I would say that Jess is methodical, responsive, and transparent when it comes to the business side of things which made a huge difference as we started to juggle more and more tasks in advance of our wedding. Jessica is simply the best. We feel so lucky to have met her and been able to work with her and her husband (who was the 2nd shooter at our wedding!).

originalText.text: Jessica was the photographer for my wedding. She did an absolute wonderful job from start to finish! We worked with her for over a year between the engagement photos and wedding photos and she was extremely helpful, caring, courteous, professional, and skilled. Jessica walked us through the process step by step and took as much time as we needed to feel comfortable. She is one of the most pleasant and caring individuals I have ever met. Her photography is incredible. The moments she captured and quality of the photos are outstanding. I strongly recommend Jessica. She is simply the best.
